---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout>
  <main class="grid grid-flow-row overflow-hidden mt-[-4rem]">
    <!-- HERO SECTION -->
    <div
      class="grid grid-rows-12 h-[100dvh] bg-[url('/img/hero.jpg')] bg-no-repeat bg-cover bg-[center] text-white"
    >
      <div
        class="row-start-9 row-end-12
      md:row-start-8 md:row-end-12
      text-center font-sans"
      >
        <header class="flex flex-col gap-2">
          <p class="text-4xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-8xl font-semibold">
            SOLVE YOUR PROBLEMS
          </p>
          <p class="text-4xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-8xl font-semibold">
            AT THE ROOT
          </p>
          <div class="">
            <a
              href="/services/"
              class="p-2 rounded-lg text-xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl"
              >Find out how</a
            >
          </div>
        </header>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Elevator Pitch -->
    <div
      class="flex flex-col p-4 sm:p-8 gap-5 bg-violet-400 text-center items-center"
    >
      <div class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-5xl">
        No more struggling with the same patterns for years
      </div>
      <div class="text-xl sm:text-2xl lg:text-3xl">
        I am here to help you address issues on a root level
      </div>
      <div class="text-lg">
        You are an amazing self-refleced individual who's read the self help
        books, maybe even done the therapy and always knows how to give the best
        advice. but somehow you never managed to translate that into the big
        changes you want for your own life. i'll let you in on a little
        secret...true change happens when we target the subconscious mind! and
        that's exactly what i know to do best.
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Relation -->
    <div
      class="grid grid-flow-row sm:grid-flow-col grid-rows-2 sm:grid-rows-1 sm:grid-cols-2 p-4 sm:p-8 bg-red-500"
    >
      <div
        class="col-span-1 bg-[url('/img/relate.jpg')] bg-center bg-no-repeat bg-cover"
      >
      </div>

      <div
        class="flex flex-col p-4 sm:p-8 py-24 gap-5 text-center items-center"
      >
        <div class="text-xl sm:text-2xl lg:text-3xl">I know what it's like</div>
        <div class="">
          <p class="text-lg">
            I know what it's like to feel stuck in a loop, with full self
            awareness of certain behaviours, yet no actual practical ways to
            change.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg">
            I know what it's like to have this big AHA moment one day, just to
            find your self in that same old pattern the next. (Read more)
          </p>
          <!-- <button class="border rounded w-max p-2">Book Now</button> -->
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonials -->
    <div
      class="flex flex-col p-4 sm:p-8 py-8 gap-5 bg-yellow-400 overflow-auto"
    >
      <div class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-5xl sm:text-center">
        Testimonials
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex overflow-auto p-4 sm:p-8 g p-4asm:p-8 w-[800px] sm:w-full"
      >
        <div class="w-1/3">
          <div class="text-xl">Forgot my troubles</div>
          <div class="">
            In a short amount of time I went from really struggling with feeling
            depressed to forgetting that I was ever depressed. Christina's
            methods are really hands on and that's what I love about her
            approach. I really felt in control of my own process and the results
            show it.
          </div>
          <div>- Emily. Y, Entrepreneur</div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-1/3">
          <div class="text-xl">Lovely Bistro</div>
          <div class="">
            Christina doesn't settle unless she's gotten to the core. She
          </div>
          <div>- Emily. Y, Entrepreneur</div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-1/3">
          <div class="text-xl">Transported to Paris</div>
          <div class="">
            Eating here made me miss Paris so much. What a treat! I will be
            bringing my client meetings here.
          </div>
          <div>- Carly, Entrepreneur</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Offerings -->
    <div
      class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between p-4 sm:p-8 gap-5 bg-sky-500"
    >
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 sm:w-1/3">
        <div class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-5xl">
          Time to get out of that Quicksand
        </div>
        <div class="text-xl">
          I help people reprogram and heal their subconscious program patterns
          and self sabotage.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 sm:grid sm:grid-cols-3">
        <a
          class="grid grid-cols-3 sm:grid-rows-10 sm:grid-cols-1"
          href="/services/ttc"
        >
          <div
            class="w-1/3 sm:w-full sm:row-span-8 bg-[url('/img/about.jpg')] bg-cover bg-no-repeat"
          >
          </div>
          <div class="">THE BODY</div>
          <div class="">TTC - SOMATIC/ ENERGY WORK</div>
        </a>
        <a
          class="grid grid-cols-3 sm:grid-rows-10 sm:grid-cols-1"
          href="/services/iat"
        >
          <div
            class="w-1/3 sm:w-full sm:row-span-8 bg-[url('/img/about.jpg')] bg-cover bg-no-repeat"
          >
          </div>
          <div class="">THE MIND</div>
          <div class="">IAT - INTEGRATED ATTACHMENT THEORY</div>
        </a>
        <a
          class="grid grid-cols-3 sm:grid-rows-10 sm:grid-cols-1"
          href="/services/ttciat"
        >
          <div
            class="w-1/3 sm:w-full sm:row-span-8 bg-[url('/img/about.jpg')] bg-cover bg-no-repeat"
          >
          </div>
          <div class="">THE MAGIC</div>
          <div class="">IAT + TTC</div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Contact CTA -->
    <aside class="flex flex-col p-4 items-center bg-green-400">
      <h2>Interested in working together?</h2>
      <a class="flex" href="mailto:me@example.com"> Reach out </a>
    </aside>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
